<html>
<head>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/AppScripts/FileUpload.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/AppScripts/create.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/content/assets/css/custom.min.css">
    <link href="~/assets/templategrouping/templategroup.custom.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="mt-3 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="template-body bg-light p-3 col-lg-12 col-sm-12 row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4">
                <label>Select a mode of file Upload:</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="fileMode">
                    <option value="0">Select private template location</option>
                    <option value="1">Local drive</option>
                    <option value="2">Https URL</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8 col-lg-8 d-none" id="zipUpload">
                <p>Upload the template file that you have generated earlier for generating your demo. If you do not have the template file, you can create the template using the <a href="../Extractor/Index" target="_blank"> Template Builder</a></p>
                <div class="form-group"><label>Upload archive file:</label><input class="form-control" type="file" id="FileUpload1" accept=".zip" /></div>
                <div id="btnContainer"><button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnUpload">Select this template</button></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8 col-lg-8 d-none" id="urlUpload">
                <p>Upload the template file that you have generated earlier for generating your demo. If you do not have the template file, you can create the template using the <a href="../Extractor/Index" target="_blank"> Template Builder</a></p>
                <div class="form-group"><label>Zip file URL:</label><input class="form-control" type="text" id="FileUpload2" placeholder="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/templatefile.zip" /></div>
                <div id="urlbtnContainer"><button class="btn btn-primary" id="importFromURL">Import from here</button><span style="color:red" id="urlerror"></span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $('#fileMode').change(function () {
            var selectedVal = $('#fileMode option:selected').val();
            if (selectedVal === "0") {
                $('#zipUpload').addClass('d-none');
                $('#urlUpload').addClass('d-none');
            }
            else if (selectedVal === "1") {
                $('#zipUpload').removeClass('d-none');
                $('#urlUpload').addClass('d-none');
            }
            else if (selectedVal === "2") {
                $('#zipUpload').addClass('d-none');
                $('#urlUpload').removeClass('d-none');
            }
        });
    });
</script>
